oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Phillips and Kirk family homes
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Photograph of the Kirk and Phillips family homes located on South Spring Street. Both homes feature wrap-around porches. The house on the left belonged to the Phillips family and the house of the right belonged to the Kirk Family.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: Looking Back at Tennessee Photograph Collection, 1890-1981
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Homes; Porches
